snippet: Stacy Lewis shot a five-under-par 68 to maintain a two-stroke lead over Brittany Lang after the second round of the Reignwood L.P.G.A. Classic in Beijing.
abstract: Stacy Lewis takes second-round lead at the Reignwood LPGA Classic in Beijing; other golf news noted.
